rank_change_df <- read.csv(paste0(folder, input_fp_lst["bootstrap_df.csv"][[1]])) %>%
  group_by(dynasty, neighbor) %>%
  summarize(
    lower=quantile(rank, na.rm=TRUE)[2],
    middle=quantile(rank, na.rm=TRUE)[3],
    upper=quantile(rank, na.rm=TRUE)[4],
    ymin=quantile(rank, na.rm=TRUE)[1],
    ymax=quantile(rank, na.rm=TRUE)[5]
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    lower=ifelse(is.na(lower), 0, lower),
    middle=ifelse(is.na(middle), 0, middle),
    upper=ifelse(is.na(upper), 0, upper),
    ymin=ifelse(is.na(ymin), 0, ymin),
    ymax=ifelse(is.na(ymax), 0, ymax)
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    neighbor_dynasty=paste0(neighbor, "_", dynasty)
  )
## `summarise()` regrouping output by 'dynasty' (override with `.groups` argument)

dyna_ranks_df <- lapply(dynasty_lst, function(dyna){
    dyna_ranks_df <- read.csv(paste0(folder, input_fp_lst["ranks_df.csv"][[1]])) %>%
    filter(dynasty==dyna & rank <= 10) %>%
    select(iter, neighbor, rank) %>%
    spread(key=iter, value=neighbor) %>%
    mutate(dynasty=dyna)
  
  return(dyna_ranks_df)
}) %>%
  bind_rows()

get_jaccard <- function(a, b) {
    intersection <- length(intersect(a, b))
    union <- length(a) + length(b) - intersection
    
    return(intersection/union)
}

jaccard_mean_df <- lapply(c(2, 5, 10, 15, 20, 25), function(topn){
    jaccard_mean_lst <- c()
    for(dyna in dynasty_lst){
      a <- fixed_df %>% filter(dynasty==dyna) %>% head(topn) %>% pull(neighbor)
      
      jaccard_lst <- c()
      for(it in 1:50){
        b <- dyna_ranks_df %>% filter(dynasty==dyna, rank<=topn) %>% pull(as.character(it))
        jaccard <- round(get_jaccard(a, b), 4)
        jaccard_lst <- c(jaccard_lst, jaccard)
      }
      jaccard_mean_lst <- c(jaccard_mean_lst, round(mean(jaccard_lst), 4))
    }
    
    jaccard_mean_df <- data.frame(
      dynasty=dynasty_lst,
      jaccard_mean=jaccard_mean_lst,
      Top=topn
    )
    return(jaccard_mean_df)
}) %>%
  bind_rows()

jaccard_mean_df$dynasty <- factor(jaccard_mean_df$dynasty, levels=dynasty_lst,
                                  labels=gsub("_seg", "\n(word-segmented)", dynasty_lst))

p_jaccard_similarity <- ggplot(jaccard_mean_df, aes(x=dynasty, y=jaccard_mean, fill=factor(Top))) +
  labs(x="Dynasty", y="Jaccard similarity", fill="Top N\nneareast\nneighbors")

p_jaccard_similarity +
  geom_bar(stat="identity", position="dodge") +
  scale_fill_viridis(discrete = TRUE)

ggsave(output_fp_lst["jaccard_similarity"][[1]])

stability_df <- lapply(dynasty_lst, function(dynasty){
  path <- paste0("/Users/mac/Documents/in_sync_mac/in_sync_documents/data/diachronic_semantics_preprocessing/",
                 dynasty, "/",
                 gsub("_seg", "", dynasty), "_boot_embed/stability_measure.json")
  
  df <- fromJSON(path) %>%
    as.data.frame() %>%
    melt(variable.name="neighbor", value.name="sim") %>%
    group_by(neighbor) %>%
    mutate(iter=row_number()) %>%
    ungroup() %>%
    mutate(
      query_word="",
      dynasty=dynasty,
      sim=round(sim, 4)
    ) %>%
    select(dynasty, query_word, neighbor, iter, sim)
  return(df)
}) %>% bind_rows()
## No id variables; using all as measure variables
## No id variables; using all as measure variables
## No id variables; using all as measure variables
## No id variables; using all as measure variables
## No id variables; using all as measure variables
## No id variables; using all as measure variables
## No id variables; using all as measure variables
stability_df <- stability_df %>%
  mutate(iter_grp=((iter-1)%/%2.5 + 1)*2.5) %>%
  #mutate(iter_grp=iter) %>%
  group_by(dynasty, neighbor, iter_grp) %>%
  summarise(grp_sim=round(mean(sim), 4)) %>%
  group_by(dynasty, iter_grp) %>%
  summarise(grp_sim=round(mean(grp_sim), 4)) %>%
  mutate(
    dynasty_grp=ifelse(grepl("1980s", dynasty), "Modern", "Pre-modern")
  )
## `summarise()` regrouping output by 'dynasty', 'neighbor' (override with `.groups` argument)
## `summarise()` regrouping output by 'dynasty' (override with `.groups` argument)
stability_df$dynasty <- factor(stability_df$dynasty, levels=dynasty_lst,
                               labels=gsub("_seg", "\n(word-segmented)", dynasty_lst))

stability_df$dynasty_grp <- factor(stability_df$dynasty_grp, levels=c("Pre-modern", "Modern"))

anno_df <- data.frame(
    dynasty_grp=c("Pre-modern", "Modern"),
    yintercept=c(0.085, 0.3)
  )

anno_df$dynasty_grp <- factor(anno_df$dynasty_grp, c("Pre-modern", "Modern"))


p_stability <- ggplot(stability_df, aes(iter_grp, grp_sim)) +
  geom_line(aes(group=dynasty), alpha=0.9) +
  geom_point(aes(shape=dynasty, group=dynasty)) +
  geom_vline(xintercept=25, linetype="dotted", color="blue") +
  geom_text(data=anno_df, aes(x=25+12.5, y=yintercept, label="Iteration = 25"), color="blue", show.legend=FALSE) +
  scale_x_continuous(limit=c(0, 50), breaks=seq(0, 50, 5)) +
  facet_wrap(vars(dynasty_grp), scale="free") +
  labs(x="Iterations", y="Stability", shape="Dynasty")

print(p_stability)
